{"tid":958240,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"邊度可以買到真正嘅 手辦 動漫 figure (含圖)","createTime":"2018-12-27T15:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T09:18:50.000Z","uid":110375,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"334a17435382d6b0bcce5995db00e7f47d6e5289","tid":958240,"uid":110375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:44:28.000Z","msg":"買figure嗰時 啲人成日話手辦公仔<br />\n<br />\n點知一上網搵 原來而家嘅手辦 公仔 都係用機器整出嚟一式一樣咁樣上色<br />\n<br />\n但係我心目中想要嘅手辦公仔 係可能人哋 有啲手手腳腳頭頭都係自己整出嚟， 或者佢哋係買 工廠嘅原蛋白色嘅figure 再自己想識有自己一套風格嘅figure<br />\n<br />\n想問下上網用啲咩關鍵字眼可以搵到呢一啲 手辦figure 香港有冇鋪頭係專賣呢<br />\n啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢幾隻我自己好鍾意 都覺得好靚但係想要啲 獨一無二啲嘅貴啲唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY0gsvS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPY0gsvS.jpg&h=d4028782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsLTuKd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsLTuKd.jpg&h=382a9487&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QSnq5hA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQSnq5hA.jpg&h=29635f1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d60ffcbefd8be758c6067a27a98b55c337a078fa","tid":958240,"uid":126619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"你想買上左色/ 未上色的?<br />\n<br />\n未上色白件淘寶一定有  想係香港買可以搵模魂之城"},{"pid":"6fdc2273ab8f10056f6d2e49679d9c68a2a41904","tid":958240,"uid":47287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"買就唔會獨一無二<br />\n支持樓主自制<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9afb3ff924e25ca94e13b78be5250481f35413f","tid":958240,"uid":110375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d60ffcbefd8be758c6067a27a98b55c337a078fa","tid":958240,"uid":126619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"你想買上左色/ 未上色的?<br />\n<br />\n未上色白件淘寶一定有  想係香港買可以搵模魂之城"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018